data.text:
In the spirit of 70’s comedy albums by artists such as Lily Tomlin, Richard Pryor and Steve Martin, The Bored Identity is a collection of characters and songs by the underground’s beloved subversive comedic performance artist. Dynasty Handbag takes on the self care industrial complex, murderous misogyny and the horrors of heteronormativity by deftly moving in and out of a crackpot slew of characters in ridiculously imaginative scenarios.

Pink vinyl. Only 500 made. Comes with a full color poster!

Only $29.99. Or if you want some socks you can get both for $39.99!
